HUN-GRR turned to WHEELIE, "I will show you my hunger when I feast on
your remains scrappling!" He said as he turned to face WHEELIE.

BLOT and the other TERRORCONS nodded as well as they too turned to WHEELIE.

"Terrorcons no eat Wheelie!" GRIMLOCK said as came to stand in between
WHEELIE and HUN-GRR, the other DINOBOTS coming around as well as
weapons came to the fore!

"We Dinobots smash!" SLAG said emphatically.

Then there was a rumble and a light quaking.

"What is that?" BACKSTOP said as he pointed, and in the distance, many
miles away one of the mountains  that trevveresed this region was
beginng to smoke as the top of it was turning red and motes of fire
broiled up!
